extendedInfo.description: Each year Contact East brings the very best of Atlantic Canadian talent, in theatre, music, and dance, to gather and showcase their work for regional, national and international buyers in attendance. This year Contact East 2013 marks the event's 22st edition.This app is your guide to everything the conference has to offer, it includes:-directions & GPS map with key locations-a full listing of delegates, events and key dates-artist bios, photos and sharing to Twitter and Facebook-access to the Contact East Facebook page and Twitter stream-ContactCam: enhance your pictures with a souvenir frame and post them to Facebook and Twitter or email
